Description:
You arrive at a camp on the edge of the gorge.

From here you can see the spectacular stone door carved into the wall of the gorge. In order to go there, you would need a rope to descend the gorge.

It seems that this camp belonged to the felines and they abandoned it some time ago to go to the more fertile lands of the southern oasis.
DescriptionAction: This may be a good time to regain your strength.
